<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201202/1c7b5dbf2c0b4da18090efbd813a2ed9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>3、负重深蹲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201202/e2c14b9ed41046859ffc7cafc54d5926.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
